These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
House: cape-cod, wooden
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani
There 2 different types of food: plum, lettuce
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, subway
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person eating plum is the pakistani##1
5. the wooden house is on the far left##1
6. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| House   | wooden   | cape-cod  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian |
| Food           | plum      | lettuce     |
| Transport     | subway    | airplane   |

